     1|/**
     2| * Pure, runtime-free helpers for merging the IVX Owner AI conversation from its
     3| * two durable sources (remote Supabase rows + the local AsyncStorage shadow) and
     4| * for bounding the local shadow so it never grows without limit.
     5| *
     6| * This module deliberately has ZERO runtime imports (only a type-only import that
     7| * is erased at build time) so the conversation-state logic can be unit-tested
